        <item>
            <title>用家分享 iPhone 15 Pro Max 影演唱會，坐後排用 25x 變焦瞬間變頭排</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/iphone-15-pro-6/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-15-pro-6</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/iphone-15-pro-6/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 03:07:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1202352</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>有不少人觀看演唱會時會用手機拍攝過程，但坐在舞台遠處的觀眾所拍攝的影片難免會十分模糊。不過有社交平台 TikTok 的用家分享，若使用 iPhone 15 的變焦功能同樣能獲得像在第一排拍攝的影像。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-1202378" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-31-17.44.41-296x580.png" alt="" width="156" height="305" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-31-17.44.41-296x580.png 296w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-31-17.44.41.png 452w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 156px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-1202379" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-31-17.45.39-324x580.png" alt="" width="170" height="304" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-31-17.45.39-324x580.png 324w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-31-17.45.39.png 430w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 170px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-1202380" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-31-17.45.56-335x580.png" alt="" width="176" height="305" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-31-17.45.56-335x580.png 335w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-31-17.45.56.png 470w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 176px" /></p><p>有 TikTok 用家分享他們在 Lana Del Rey、Coldplay、Travis Scott 和 Tate Mcrae 演唱會上使用 iPhone 15 Zoom 後，所拍攝的影像等同坐在舞台的第一排，非常清晰。</p><p>其中一段觀看次數超過 5530 萬次的 TikTok 影片中，TikTok 用户 Anthony Xavier 利用 iPhone 15 Zoom 拍攝樂團 Coldplay 演唱會的情況，更特意縮小鏡頭放大倍數以證明其離舞台非常遠。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@anthony.xavier/video/7285453773063933217" data-video-id="7285453773063933217" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 325px;" ><section><a target="_blank" title="@anthony.xavier" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@anthony.xavier?refer=embed">@anthony.xavier</a></p><p>@coldplay at Rose Bowl <a title="iphone15promax" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/iphone15promax?refer=embed">#iphone15promax</a><a title="coldplay" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/coldplay?refer=embed">#coldplay</a></p><p><a target="_blank" title="♬ original sound - AnthonyXavier" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7285453834468576033?refer=embed">♬ original sound &#8211; AnthonyXavier</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></div><p>Apple 今年 9 月推出全新 iPhone 15 系列手機，其中 iPhone 15 Pro Max 配備了能夠進行 5 倍光學變焦的四稜鏡鏡頭，而 iPhone 15 Pro 新更新的 5 倍光學變焦比上一代 iPhone 14 中的 3 倍變焦高出許多。另外據 Apple 指，當啟用 5 倍光學變焦時，用户還可以啟用最高 25 倍的數碼變焦。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://petapixel.com/2023/10/30/concertgoers-use-iphone-15-zoom-for-front-row-feeling-amid-high-ticket-prices/">petapixel</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/iphone-15-pro-6/fun-tech/">用家分享 iPhone 15 Pro Max 影演唱會，坐後排用 25x 變焦瞬間變頭排</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/iphone-15-pro-6/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
